{"tid":2463054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"暴動案候審長達兩三年 還柙被告隨時「白坐」 大狀嘆不公道","createTime":"2021-03-26T11:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T14:52:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":27,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"b69d5c955492da96e5ba7f297ab7aa179247ea54","tid":2463054,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:54:06.000Z","msg":"法庭積壓大量抗爭案件，目前有案件排期到2024年才能審訊，今日提訊的立法會暴動案亦要整整兩年後才開審。有大律師指出，近期暴動案定罪後多數判監4至5年，被告服刑期間行為良好的話，一般服刑約3年後便可出獄。如果被告須還柙，受審後被定罪，則可能毋須再服刑；但一旦獲判無罪，「呢三年佢白坐㗎啦喎，你講緊三年，唔係坐多咗幾個月。」大狀批評有如未審先判，對被告不公道。<br />\n<br />\n至於獲准保釋的被告，也要遵守宵禁、禁足、不准離港等條件。大狀對此不敢苟同，質疑法庭將「所有辣招都加於同一個人身上」，擾亂被告生活之餘，「好似係純粹懲罰佢在先咁樣。」觀乎其他刑事案件的被吿，也未必需要遵守繁多保釋條件，「我都唔係好明白點解而家暴動啲（保釋）條件要咁多。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然被告可以向高等法院申請保釋，或是申請放寬保釋條件，惟大狀慨嘆謂，法庭處理示威案有另一套準則，形容此為高壓政策，「好似用緊第二本law book咁。」大狀續指，不少還柙的示威者被告都有良好背景，惟他們的保釋申請被拒；即使是獲准保釋的被告要求更改擔保條件，也可能遭法庭質疑：「俾你（保釋）仲咁多嘢講，信唔信我唔俾你吖嗱？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210326/WWXAESVWLBCGXDRMFJYGDOCDRE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210326%2FWWXAESVWLBCGXDRMFJYGDOCDRE%2F&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=e9f454bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210326%2FWWXAESVWLBCGXDRMFJYGDOCDRE%2F&h=4d770d3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210326/WWXAESVWLBCGXDRMFJYGDOCDRE/</a>"},{"pid":"783487638c667e7548bd73a87938c9454b16c75c","tid":2463054,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e615ae6e4e42d75f95b6e94318e95777b8b02765","tid":2463054,"uid":106544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc5888b56e5b19c37126f6d77d5a1e303637df5","tid":2463054,"uid":36178,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:00:49.000Z","msg":"OMDB"},{"pid":"39e7706f8b55923e56e84e633ed3785a4b97ccdb","tid":2463054,"uid":118988,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:01:01.000Z","msg":"香港特色的司法獨立"},{"pid":"18f60fcff9e3ee1c6c5448edfd1f163c79bafc4e","tid":2463054,"uid":108337,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:02:34.000Z","msg":"雖然係咁，不過法治未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77bf50be1fc4d607684f9ebc82e0804b11a3b18","tid":2463054,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:02:47.000Z","msg":"呢啲多數都係屌完就算唔會有啲咩實質行動"},{"pid":"993fad16685fe92a6883db7f38ae162cce0b67c3","tid":2463054,"uid":50931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18f60fcff9e3ee1c6c5448edfd1f163c79bafc4e","tid":2463054,"uid":108337,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:02:34.000Z","msg":"雖然係咁，不過法治未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"之前邊樹吹風話要課金支持培養多啲新晉大狀幫手足？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c5bfa0fab9829e583a85197e10a4fef3825994","tid":2463054,"uid":131084,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:09:29.000Z","msg":"香港而家嘅司法制度就係告你唔入都一樣坐幾年"},{"pid":"317479e4c86fd1be0b7180cf3f358410521c4db6","tid":2463054,"